      DEN
    room/den/

                        LEGEND:
        
        M* = drug salesman / wholesale buyer 
        (room/den/den5.c, npc/pusherman.c)
        
        D* = hidden button to move player to E*
          (room/den/den9.c -> room/fhall1.c)
        
        E* = entrance to hidden facility / back to den
            (room/fhall1.c -> room/den/den9.c) 
        
        V* = hidden loot that can be found by players
                (/room/vip/vip6 & vip8)

        F* = keycard slot for accessing vip area / trap room
                (rooms/fhall4.c, rooms/deathpit.c,)          

        P* = hidden switch that moves player to quest room
           (room/processing/proc6.c -> room/questroom.c)

        Q* = hidden quest mob for starting / finishing quest
             (room/questroom.c, npc/smuggler_quest.c)

        S* = entrance to the boss room
         (room/vip/vip7.c -> room/vip/saferoom.c)

        B* = boss room / quest item location (search drawer)
             (rooms/vip/saferoom.c, obj/recipe_quest.c)